{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build your career from the ground up, steadily climbing the corporate ladder while balancing the demands of work with the joys and challenges of life outside of the office.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437260/extras/Video_Gameplay_Laptop_Ummugif.gif?t=1738290151\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pay close attention during interviews\u2014are the candidates being honest with what they sayl? Review their CVs, ask the right questions, and decide whether to approve or reject their applications based on your instincts and observations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437260/extras/Interview_gif.gif?t=1738290151\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find a way to achieve your Productivity Point target from your boss. Check carefully about your budget and how you're gonna spend it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437260/extras/Fire_karyawangif.gif?t=1738290151\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sometimes, being an HR professional means making tough choices. If firing someone is necessary to achieve your target, it\u2019s up to you to make that call and face the consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437260/extras/Jack_Traininggif.gif?t=1738290151\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But firing isn't always an option, you can train your employees to increase their productivity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437260/extras/night_mode_gif.gif?t=1738290151\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">During the day, you\u2019ll work hard to meet your boss\u2019s expectations. At night, unwind with your cat, reconnect with family, or simply take a moment to rest and recharge. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437260/extras/mood_gif.gif?t=1738290151\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Overworking isn't an option. You need to try to maintain your mood to keep productivity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437260/extras/variation_gif.gif?t=1738290151\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In office life, you will meet lots of different types of employees. Collect them all and complete your compendium.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437260/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738290151","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437260/page.bg.jpg?t=1738290151","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437260/7dc6e19a9d1012f63e690ccb472de277726a7a50/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738290151","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437260/7dc6e19a9d1012f63e690ccb472de277726a7a50/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738290151","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},